[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0208","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0208.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0489","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5.0 文件上传控件脚本粘贴漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 5.0 的 MSHTML.DLL 组件存在未信任脚本粘贴漏洞（untrusted scripted paste）。远程攻击者可通过构造特制网页，利用脚本将任意文件名粘贴至文件上传内置控件中，绕过用户交互限制，实现恶意文件的上传操作。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系统上运行的 IE 5.0 浏览器，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。Microsoft 已在 MS98-013 安全公告中提供修复措施。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0489"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-05-17T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:30.367","remediation":"建议升级 Internet Explorer 至 5.01 以上版本，微软已在 MS98-013 公告中修复该问题。当前所有受支持 Windows 版本均已内置更新版 IE，建议用户升级至现代浏览器（如 Edge/Chrome）以避免此漏洞。如无法升级，可在 IE 安全设置中将「Internet 区域」的「对未标记为可安全执行脚本的 ActiveX 控件初始化并执行脚本」设为「禁用」以降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-015"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0208.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0884","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0884.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1029","title":"SSH Communications Security sshd2 密码暴力破解漏洞","description":"SSH服务器sshd2 2.0.12之前版本存在认证记录缺失漏洞。当攻击者在达到最大尝试次数前主动关闭连接，服务端未能正确记录此次登录尝试，导致暴力破解行为不会出现在审计日志中。远程攻击者可利用此缺陷绕过审计机制，通过大量密码枚举尝试获取系统访问权限，严重影响系统安全性。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1029"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:33.427","remediation":"升级 sshd2 至 2.0.12 或更高版本，该版本已正确记录所有登录尝试次数。同时可配置系统日志审计、部署 fail2ban 等暴力破解防护工具，并限制 SSH 登录尝试频率与来源 IP，增强暴力破解检测能力。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92663402004280&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/277","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2193","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1029.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1029","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1029.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1029.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1029.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6mfv-3x79-9r84/GHSA-6mfv-3x79-9r84.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/277/info.html","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-223.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0884.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0507","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0507.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0776","title":"阿里巴巴 HTTP 服务器目录遍历漏洞","description":"阿里巴巴 HTTP 服务器存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过在 URL 中添加 \"../\" 等路径穿越序列，绕过访问限制读取服务器上的任意文件。该漏洞源于服务器对用户提供的文件路径过滤不严，未对 \"../\" 等特殊字符进行有效校验。攻击者无需身份认证，仅需构造特制 HTTP 请求即可利用，可能导致敏感信息泄露。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0776"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:02.090","remediation":"立即停止使用已停止维护的阿里巴巴 HTTP Server，迁移至 Apache HTTP Server 或 Nginx 等活跃维护的 Web 服务器。如无法立即替换，在反向代理或 WAF 层面拦截包含 \"/../\" 的 URL 请求路径作为临时缓解。升级到最新补丁版本（如有）或彻底移除该服务器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ntbugtraq.com/default.asp?pid=36&sid=1&A2=ind9905&L=NTBUGTRAQ&P=R1533"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0507.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0017","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0017.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0229","title":"Microsoft Windows NT IIS 目录遍历拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 服务器存在路径遍历拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过向目标服务器发送包含特殊构造的 `..\\..` 序列的 HTTP 请求触发目录遍历，导致服务器资源耗尽或崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系统上的 Microsoft IIS 服务，利用方式简单，危害性较高。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0229"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-05-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:57.530","remediation":"升级至 Windows 2000 及以上版本（含 IIS 5.0+），或在 Windows NT 4.0 上安装 IIS 4.0 Service Pack 及 MS98-004 安全补丁。如无法升级，在 IIS 管理器中禁用未使用的虚拟目录并移除可执行权限以缓解风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0229","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0229.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0229","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0229.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0229.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0229.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-79m3-vm8c-387r/GHSA-79m3-vm8c-387r.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/I/iis_crash.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x3000/2218/info.html","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-02xx/CVE-1999-0229.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0017.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0887","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0887.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1033","title":"Microsoft Outlook Express POP3 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Outlook Express 4.72.3612.1700 之前版本存在 POP3 协议处理缺陷，远程攻击者可通过发送包含特殊构造的 \"..\" 字符串的恶意邮件，诱使 Outlook 重新进入 POP3 命令模式，导致 POP3 会话挂起无法继续处理后续邮件，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Outlook Express 4.27.3110 及 4.72.3120 等版本，攻击者无需认证即可触发，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1033"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:33.953","remediation":"将 Microsoft Outlook Express 升级至 4.72.3612.1700 或更高版本，此版本修复了包含 \"..\" 序列的恶意邮件导致 POP3 命令模式循环挂起的问题。如无法升级，建议禁用 POP3 邮箱功能或改用 IMAP 协议收信作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92647407427342&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92663402004275&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/252","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19207","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1033.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1033.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1033","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1033.json","https://github.com/xaitax/SploitScan/blob/e7c7a6140bbd6a60ea622b6124620fbed9d12332/README.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1033.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1033.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-935q-jf44-fq38/GHSA-935q-jf44-fq38.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0887.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0608","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0608.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0754","title":"ISC INN inndstart 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"INN（InterNetNews）新闻服务器中的 inndstart 程序存在权限提升漏洞，本地攻击者可通过设置 INNCONF 环境变量指定恶意配置文件，从而以提升后的权限执行任意操作。该漏洞影响早期版本的 INN 新闻服务器软件，攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限，利用方式简单，可导致系统完全受控。建议升级至最新版本以修复此漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0754"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:59.240","remediation":"升级 INN 至 2.2 及以上版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。无法升级时，移除 inndstart 的 SUID 位（chmod u-s /usr/bin/inndstart），或限制用户对 INNCONF 环境变量的设置权限，避免低权限用户通过该变量加载恶意配置文件提升权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.redhat.com/corp/support/errata/inn99_05_22.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/255"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0608.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0501","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0501.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0773","title":"Sun Solaris 7.0 lpset 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 7.0 的 /usr/bin/lpset 程序中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地低权限用户可通过向该程序提交特制的参数或环境变量触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖内存空间，从而获取 root 权限，完全控制目标系统。该漏洞影响 Sun Solaris 7.0 版本，攻击者需具有本地登录权限，无需网络访问即可完成提权利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0773"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:01.700","remediation":"安装 Sun 官方补丁 106980（Solaris 7 适用），或升级至 Solaris 8 及以上版本。临时缓解措施：以 root 执行 `chmod 555 /usr/bin/lpset` 移除 setuid 位，限制本地普通用户以提权方式运行该程序。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.netspace.org/cgi-bin/wa?A2=ind9905B&L=bugtraq&P=R2017","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19206"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0501.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0514","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0514.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0785","title":"ISC INN inndstart 程序 pathrun 参数本地权限提升漏洞","description":"ISC (Internet Software Consortium) 的 INN (InterNetNews) 软件中的 inndstart 程序存在权限管理缺陷，当 pathrun 参数在 inn.conf 文件中配置时，本地用户可以利用该参数以 root 权限执行任意程序，实现本地权限提升。攻击者必须是本地用户，能够修改 inn.conf 配置文件或触发 inndstart 读取恶意配置。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0785"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-11","updated":"2024-06-16","remediation":"升级到 INN 最新版本，限制 inndstart 程序的 setuid 权限，并确保 inn.conf 配置文件仅允许受信任的管理员修改，避免 pathrun 参数被非授权用户控制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/254"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0514.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0568","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0568.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0806","title":"Sun Solaris dtprintinfo 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 7.0 系统中的 dtprintinfo 工具存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，该程序位于 /usr/dt/bin/dtprintinfo，在处理特制输入时未正确验证缓冲区边界，导致可被利用覆盖内存数据。本地攻击者可通过向 dtprintinfo 传递超长参数触发溢出，进而以 root 权限执行任意代码，实现权限提升。该漏洞影响 Solaris 7.0 版本，需本地访问权限，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0806"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-10T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:05.767","remediation":"安装 Sun 官方补丁 107080-01（SPARC 平台）或 107081-01（x86 平台）修复 dtprintinfo 缓冲区溢出漏洞。若无法打补丁，立即移除 dtprintinfo 的 setuid 位：chmod -s /usr/dt/bin/dtprintinfo，或限制仅管理员可执行：chmod 700 /usr/dt/bin/dtprintinfo。如不需要 CDE 打印功能可直接删除该二进制文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6552","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19205"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0568.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0568.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0568.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0356","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0356.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0738","title":"Microsoft Internet Information Server code.asp 示例文件任意文件读取漏洞","description":"IIS 和 Site Server 中自带的 code.asp 示例文件存在任意文件读取漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的 HTTP 请求，利用该示例文件读取服务器上的任意文件内容，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Microsoft IIS 及 Site Server 的多个版本，攻击条件低，无需身份认证即可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0738"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:57.270","remediation":"立即删除 IIS 及 Site Server 中 code.asp、showcode.asp、viewcode.asp 等示例文件查看器（默认不安装于 IIS，但在 Site Server 中默认安装），或安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-013 提供的补丁。作为临时缓解措施，可通过 NTFS ACL 严格限制这些文件的读取权限，并将示例文件移出 Web 内容目录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-013"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0356.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0355","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0355.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0737","title":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 showcode.asp 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 中的 showcode.asp 示例脚本存在任意文件读取漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过构造特制的 HTTP 请求查看服务器上的任意文件内容，导致系统配置文件、源代码等敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 IIS 4.0 及 Site Server 相关版本，利用方式简单，危害等级中等，Microsoft 已在后续更新中建议删除该示例脚本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0737"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:57.140","remediation":"删除 IIS 安装目录下的 `\\IIS Samples\\Scripts` 目录及其所有文件，特别是 `showcode.asp` 和 `viewcode.asp` 等示例脚本。对于生产环境，不应部署任何 IIS 示例文件。同时确认 IIS 虚拟目录中未映射非必要的脚本映射（如 `.htr`、`.idc` 等）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-013"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0355.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0352","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0352.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0736","title":"Microsoft IIS showcode.asp 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"IIS 和 Site Server 中默认安装的 showcode.asp 示例文件存在任意文件读取漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过向目标服务器发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可利用该漏洞读取服务器上的任意文件，包括系统配置文件、源代码等敏感信息。该漏洞影响 Microsoft IIS 4.0 及 Site Server 3.0 版本，属于信息泄露类安全风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0736"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:57.020","remediation":"删除 IIS 安装目录下的 `showcode.asp` 示例文件（通常位于 `\\InetPub\\wwwroot\\Samples\\`），或移除整个 Samples 虚拟目录。升级至 IIS 5.0 及以上版本以彻底消除该旧版示例文件带来的风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-013","https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A932","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19129"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0352.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0245","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0245.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0686","title":"Netscape Enterprise Server HP-UX 平台长 URL 请求拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Netscape Enterprise Server（NES）在 HP-UX 平台的 HP Virtual Vault（VVOS）环境中存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制超长 URL 请求，触发服务进程崩溃或资源耗尽，导致服务器无法正常处理合法用户请求。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程利用，攻击门槛较低，主要影响 HP Virtual Vault 操作系统上运行的 NES Web 服务，在特定网络条件下可造成拒绝服务。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0686"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-05-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:50.783","remediation":"建议立即升级 Netscape Enterprise Server 至 3.6 SP2 及以上版本（HP-UX 对应安全补丁编号 PHSS_20316）。在反向代理或负载均衡器（如 HP-UX Apache-based Web Server）上限制 URL 长度不超过 4096 字节，拒绝超过阈值的请求。配置 WAF 规则过滤包含超长路径的 HTTP 请求。由于 NES 及 HP-UX Virtual Vault 均已停止技术支持，长期解决方案应迁移至受支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server）和操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-046.shtml","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9906-098","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0686.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0686","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0686.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0686.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mrj2-v329-4cm9/GHSA-mrj2-v329-4cm9.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0686.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0245.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0245.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0357","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0357.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0739","title":"Microsoft IIS codebrws.asp 示例文件任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 及 Site Server 中的 codebrws.asp 示例文件存在任意文件读取漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标服务器发送特制 HTTP 请求，利用该示例文件读取系统上的任意文件（如配置文件、源代码等），导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 IIS 及 Site Server 多个版本，攻击复杂度较低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0739"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-07","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"删除 IIS 及 Site Server 中不需要的示例 ASP 文件（包括 codebrws.asp、showcode.asp、viewcode.asp、code.asp），生产环境不应保留任何示例脚本。若必须使用这些文件查看器功能，请安装 Microsoft 提供的安全补丁 MS99-013，并确保 Web 站点目录权限配置为最小权限原则。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-013","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0739"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0357.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0316","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0316.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0717","title":"Microsoft Excel 97 病毒警告机制禁用漏洞","description":"Microsoft Excel 97 存在病毒警告机制可被远程攻击者禁用的安全漏洞。攻击者可通过构造包含恶意宏的特制 Excel 文件，诱使用户打开后绕过内置的病毒警告提示，使得恶意宏在未获用户确认的情况下自动执行。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Excel 97 版本，攻击者需诱导用户打开恶意文件方可利用，CVSS 评分 2.6，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0717"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-07","updated":"1999-05-07","remediation":"下载并安装微软 MS99-014 安全公告提供的 Excel 97 补丁（Xl8p9pkg），或升级至 Excel 2000 及以上版本（已内置修复）。建议将 Excel 宏安全级别设置为「高」，并禁止自动加载不受信任来源的外部文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ231304","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-014"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0316.toml"}]